\FF[yuri_smile]Yurika: "Me...? What are you trying to say...?"

\F[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "That's right, Akane. The president has always
been helping us..."

\F[sirius_angry2]Akane: "Pretending to help while actually observing us
closely. You must have realized that."

\F[sirius_angry2]Akane: "That I'm chasing the culprit... an agent. Yes! In
other words, I've been chasing you."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "..."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "No, that's not right... Akane. The president who
has been working hard for the school, a monster? That's
just..."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Besides, this time too... she helped us so
much!"

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "It's because Amasan's monster was also a threat to
the president. Our interests just happened to align, that's
all."
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "To say it like that..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko. There are various types of monsters. My
guess is that the student council president's preferences
are probably similar to Amasan's. The kind that uses both a
facade and what's behind it..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Are you saying I have a double face? That's quite
an insult. I live my life honestly."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I know. You're the type of monster who doesn't
hesitate to dye the world in your own colors. The most
troublesome kind."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nako_angry]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Evidence...!? When a detective names a culprit,
it should be when they have irrefutable evidence...!"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nako_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Yes, exactly."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "I'm curious too. You must have something solid to
name me with such confidence, right? I'd like to see it."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Then how about this? I know... where Wata is
hiding."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Eh...!?"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "...I see."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "You were a tough opponent. Observing carefully and
making accurate assessments... and you left no openings."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Our newbies... the agents of Banterou must have
seemed like fools to you, no doubt."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Indeed, they are clowns. They're nowhere near ready
to be out in the field. But..."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "They are professionals after all. Agents with top-
tier skills. They may be quirky and hard to handle, but...
when it's time to act, they do!"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "...! You were monitoring changes within the school
without us noticing?"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Quick thinking saves the day. You noticed the
surveillance system at the school gate, right? So I took
advantage of that!"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "The sensors inside the school don't have cameras
attached. That's why you didn't notice them. You were
looking for something like the one at the school gate, so
you couldn't have noticed."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "I've already investigated the traces of the
different space you open! So if we follow that... we can
trace it."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "So for these past few hours, your juniors running
around the school weren't dealing with Amakun... they were
flushing me out..."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "You're more cunning than I thought, Akane Suzaku. I
thought you were the type to rush in without thinking."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Also, I've been monitoring Reverse Poison's attacks
to some extent. The student council ignored the three people
running around the corridors before the attack started.
Despite complaints being raised."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Don't you think a student council that doesn't stop
students from running in the hallways is suspicious?"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "..."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "I've confirmed that you made contact with Wata
through a different world. It's thanks to Nadeshiko's great
work. Without the idea of a different world, we couldn't
have followed just with sensor information."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Is that... really true...? The president is a
monster...? And also the culprit who kidnapped Wata...?"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "She deceived us...?"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "I'm sorry. I was planning to tell you properly."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "To invite her to become the same kind of monster...?
I won't let that happen."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Monster, monster... as if everything is evil..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "There's nothing good about things done in hiding!
You know that too."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "I am..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "...Please quietly accept the Poison Burst. Let's end
this... now!"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "President..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "I must refuse. If you understand what I am doing, I
would like you to agree with me."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "You must have hidden desires in your hearts too,
right?"

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "In the 'Kingdom', you can release those desires and
still protect this peaceful everyday life. It offers a peace
of mind that bats, eels, or bitchy gals can't achieve."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "You are not suitable. Someone who runs around the
hallways without any norms... You are the very irregularity
that disrupts both 'everyday life' and the 'Kingdom'."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "...Then it seems we have no choice but to fight!"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "...I shall accept your challenge."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "I want to ask you one thing. Do you think it's...

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "If there's an unavoidable feeling, is it

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "It's not permissible! But there are times when... I

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "To think that my 'beloved' was so close by all this

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "You changed my values and allowed me to build my

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Akane: "I don't understand what's going on...!"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "The purpose of the 'Kingdom' is to grant

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "It's to provide a place where those with both

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "I thought you, who frequently masturbates alone in

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Akane: "..."
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Akane..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "But even so... when I look at you... why do I feel

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Akane: "Monkey... calling me a monkey... what do you think

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Going to the toilet so often... is that what it

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "I thought I hated it. But I was wrong! There was

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "I wanted to meet you. And..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "I wanted to monopolize you... to make you mine

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Akane: "What are you saying...!?"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Does that mean...!?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "The 'Kingdom' of the KINGDOM does not allow
monopolization. It's the source of conflict. I know it's
contradictory as a king. That's why I can't stop feeling
restless."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "But still... now that I know, there's no turning
back. I want you."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "As my partner, I want you to come to the 'Kingdom'.

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[king_ero]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Not groom but...!? No, no... there's too much
